 multiple inside a `ToggleButtonGroup` to link them with shared selection and keyboard navigation — `defaultSelectedKeys` sets the initial selection."},"868":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-31","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#multiple-selection","content":"Use `selectionMode=\"multiple\"` to allow more than one item to be active at a time."},"869":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-32","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#controlled","content":"Use `selectedKeys` and `onSelectionChange` to control selection from parent state — `onSelectionChange` receives a `Set<string>` of the selected item `id` values."},"870":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-33","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#disabled-states","content":"Disable the entire group with `isDisabled` on the container, or disable individual items with `isDisabled` on specific `ToggleButton` elements."},"871":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-34","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#sizes","content":"Two sizes are available: `sm` and `md` (default)."},"872":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-35","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon--text","content":"Items can include an `Icon` alongside text for added visual context."},"873":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-36","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon-only","content":"For compact layouts, items can contain only icons. Padding adjusts automatically to keep the button square — no extra prop required. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only item so screen readers can identify the action."},"874":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-37","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#with-dropdown","content":"Wrap a `ToggleButton` in a `MenuTrigger` to add sub-options to a group item."},"875":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-38","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#rtl-direction","content":"The group follows the document's layout direction, detected automatically from the browser locale."},"876":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-39","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"Components automatically add data attributes for styling different states:"},"877":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-40","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButtonGroup Container:** `data-size`"},"878":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-41","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#data-attributes","content":"**ToggleButton Item:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`, `data-pressed`, `data-focus-visible`, `data-disabled`"},"879":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-42","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#component-customization","content":"Individual components can be styled by passing `className` props:"},"880":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-43","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Key"},"881":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-44","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Action"},"882":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-45","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Tab**"},"883":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-46","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Moves focus to/from the button group (single tab stop)"},"884":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-47","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Arrow Left / Right**"},"885":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-48","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus between items (RAC automatically reverses in RTL)"},"886":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-49","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Space / Enter**"},"887":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-50","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Toggle the focused item"},"888":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-51","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Home**"},"889":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-52","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the first item"},"890":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-53","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**End**"},"891":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-54","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the last item"},"892":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-55","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"single\"` → `role=\"radiogroup\"` on container, `role=\"radio\"` + `aria-checked` per item"},"893":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-56","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"multiple\"` → `role=\"toolbar\"` on container, `role=\"button\"` + `aria-pressed` per item"},"894":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-57","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`aria-label` (or `aria-labelledby`) is required on the group container"},"895":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-58","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"Icon-only items require `aria-label` on each `ToggleButton`"},"896":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-59","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For grouped contextual actions — two or more closely related actions that belong together (e.g. Bold / Italic / Underline, Align Left / Center / Right)"},"897":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-60","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For compact action grouping — related actions in space-constrained layouts (e.g. Undo / Redo, Zoom In / Out / Reset)"},"898":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-61","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For multi-select scenarios — when users need to select multiple options simultaneously"},"899":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-62","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For unrelated actions that perform disconnected tasks without shared context"},"900":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-63","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For more than 5 choices — cognitive overload; consider a **Select** instead"},"901":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-64","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When actions require strong visual distinction (e.g. Save vs. Delete)"},"902":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-65","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When selecting an option leads to a different page or workflow — use navigation instead"},"903":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-66","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For mutually exclusive content views (e.g. Monthly / Yearly) — use **SegmentedController** instead"},"904":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-67","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keep-variants-consistent","content":"Avoid mixing different content types (text-only, icon-only, icon+text) within the same group. Mixing styles creates visual noise and makes the set feel fragmented rather than unified."},"905":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-68","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#balance-label-lengths","content":"Keep button labels of similar length. Large differences in text length cause irregular button wi